Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:10.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:21.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:40.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:47.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:54.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:01:00.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:08.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:15.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:22.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:29.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:48.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bell Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:56.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:14.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! You're going off course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:19.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,They failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:24.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,We failed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:46.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two have been weird since\Nthat day. Did something happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was so Rimone's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,And after they let her in\Nfor being some genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:56.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:59.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair to Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:17.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,White Loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:29.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest may be back on\Nactive duty, but in that condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's Chor Tempest's current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:38.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you give us your perspective\Nas Chor Dextra's sole survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Granted, we're not in\Na position to be optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:48.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's quite clear that this isn't the same\Nunit known as the "elite" chor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,At their current strength,\Nthe afternoon shift is their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:55.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems they can't\Nreturn to night shift soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,The team needs urgent rebuilding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:01.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you do it, Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:11.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving!\NWe're checking the helical motors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to reload the ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look here, Rimone,\Nwhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop dragging Aer down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're not motivated,\Nwhy don't you quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm here because\Nthey told me to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:33.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must be the new arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your name's... Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,During your trainee days, your\Ntalents were asserted to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:08.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since training school,\Nyou've rewritten record books...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:14.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as the youngest achiever in written\Nand practical exams, the top sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:19.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, recognizing your skills,\Nthe powers that be assigned you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:25.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the youngest sibylla, to Chor Tempest\Nas an exception among exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Combat experience... zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mobilized without\Npermission the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I was interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:43.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't need me to tell\Nyou that your dossier is ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,At least until Chor Tempest fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're feeling hesitant, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:54.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, who ever thought\Nyou'd turn into a sibylla like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Trust me, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just do as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you can\Nreturn to your past glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:14.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Back to the peak\Nwhere prodigies belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:21.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems Dominüra plans to rebuild\NChor Tempest with Rimone at its core.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:26.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, chor matters are your domain.\NI have no clue about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,No clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:34.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are those highly\Nemotional sibyllae thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:37.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's far beyond the grasp of us adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:42.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't even begin to understand\Nhow the youngest sibylla feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,How presumptuous would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:55.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we're dealing with now is a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even children can sense that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:38.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:47.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, if I said I wanted to dissolve\Nour pair, what would you think, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:48.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:53.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that's what you really want,\NRimone, I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not as though I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,If only these hands on\Nthe flight stick could be removed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, you can\Ngo over there till I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:25.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never made any\Nchoices on my own till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:30.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always done\Nwhatever others told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the next thing I knew, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:36.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I'd like you to decide for me, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:40.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you'd kill\Nsomeone if you were told to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:46.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you\Nwhat to do. Not anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm here because\NI chose not to make choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:55.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're scared of fighting,\Nyou should quit being a sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:09:00.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you want to stay here,\Nyou have to keep flying a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:08.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you really have no reason to be\Nhere, quitting's the only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, you're wonderfully talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:38.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can become\Nan amazing Simoun sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, match your partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because there isn't anyone\Nwho can keep up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't butt in just because\Nyou have a little talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:02.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:16.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why have you stopped\Nflying Simouns, Sibylla Aurea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that right now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:33.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea...\Nwhat are we all here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:51.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I am now, I can't possibly help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all that,\Nnothing's changed for me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Scout their strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:21.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems there's word of\Nsignificant military action in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:24.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the north?\NThe Plumbum highlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:29.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or rather, it's a chance to see\NDominüra and Rimone's compatibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:33.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're sending those\Ntwo along with Floe and Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have those two paired up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:42.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say it was Dominüra's decision.\NI wonder what kind of person she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is where you're sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the auriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. This is where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:00.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since that incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:18.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you've been subconsciously holding\Nback your abilities. Release them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:23.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? No one\Nknows more about you than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you do, everything will turn out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,She made Rimone the auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess she's giving it some thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well? Are you starting to get the feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:26.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Arriving at target destination shortly.\NMaintain contact as we start scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,So let's hear it, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:48.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you up to the job of auriga?\NOr are you being a pushover again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:52.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's to be\Nno talking during the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Also, never ask Rimone\Nquestions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,No wonder it's so chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right wing, no sign of aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Likewise, no sign of aircraft ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enemy at three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go too, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:41.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Rimone! A sudden\NSilver Ri Majon is too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not possible! Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:20.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your trainee days still haunt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not good. All this snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,This snowstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're late... They should've\Nbeen back a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:03.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh! Who knew there were so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:11.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can barely fly straight in this\Nsnowstorm, let alone try a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:17.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard enough for us...\Nbut those two just paired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:21.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, we're retreating. There's\Nno point if we can't do a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our mission is scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll regroup and come back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:57.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were so late we came\Nto pick you up. Situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're about to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:00.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:10.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! Do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make up your own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or are you being a pushover again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silver Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:52.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's suicidal! In these conditions...\NAnd it needs several Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silver Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,It won't work! Disengage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:41.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NWhat I wanted to achieve...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:49.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was a Ri Majon more\Nperfect than anyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:37.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did we do it?\NDid we destroy those enemy tanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:18.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's a genius after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was right about her all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:48.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:53.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:23:00.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:08.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:20.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:25.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:29.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:33.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:39.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:45.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:48.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:54.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:24:00.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:07.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:07.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued\NI'm Kaim, Sibylla Paraietta's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:10.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Kaim, Sibylla Paraietta's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:12.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama's pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:16.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:17.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wounds and Pain\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.43,0:24:20.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wounds and Pain\NWounds and Pain.
